data.description: Large Rock house tucked away in the woods down your own private drive sits on 12.017 acres.  YES - it needs a lot of work.  The house and the guest house offer over 5,900 sq ft of living space.  Main house has 4 bedrooms, 3 of which have their own bathrooms, an Office, two living areas, a Den with a dry bar , An additional room upstairs and a large concrete deck overlooking the pool.  There are three AC units all of which need to be replaced.  The guest house sits above the 2 car garage and a shop. The pool has been checked out and the pumps work.  There is a covered Cabana with a fire pit and the pool offers a swim up bar.  It is a unique lay out.  Bring your imagination.  Call to schedule a showing  This Property is part of an Estate and Being Sold AS IS.
